column12: It's okay, I'm fine... What about you?
Okay, good. ...Hey, by the way, look at this. I found it while you were gone.
No! You need to eat too.
Fine. I'll take the small half.
No. Come on, you need to keep up your strength—
Oh no... I'm sorry I dropped the cookie... I didn't mean to...
You've...always been the one...helping me, so...so I just wanted to...
Please, somebody, we need help! Help us!
